tests.title: Examples of Selectors via WebdriverUni Contact Us Page
tests.fullTitle: Selector examples Examples of Selectors via WebdriverUni Contact Us Page
tests.code:
cy.visit("http://www.webdriveruniversity.com/Contact-Us/contactus.html"); //By tag name
cy.get("input"); //By attribute name and value
cy.get("input[name='first_name']"); //By id
cy.get("#contact_me"); //By class
cy.get(".feedback-input"); //By multiple classes
cy.get("[class='navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top']"); //By two different attributes
cy.get("[name='email'][placeholder='Email Address']"); //By xpath
// Require add XPath command to Cypress test runner: npm install -D cypress-xpath
cy.xpath("//input[@name='first_name']");
